{"tid":1034885,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴克里：給沙利多點時間","createTime":"2019-02-24T08:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T14:02:51.000Z","uid":31626,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9e0b6d10e767eacbaf26d4582e2adff3ecdf9d","tid":1034885,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xbPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=9b3d92e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】車路士領隊沙利備受下台壓力，中場巴克里就希望大家給予他多點時間。<br />\n<br />\n車路士近況非常飄忽，早前曾於英超以0:6大敗予曼城，在英足盃亦被曼聯以2:0踢出局，有傳若周日英聯盃決賽未能力壓藍月封王，沙利的帥位立即不保，由助教賀蘭特頂上。<br />\n<br />\n今季在沙利麾下表現不錯的巴克里（Ross Barkley）說：「我們的目標是成為世界上其中一支最佳球員。領隊希望踢出的風格，並不是現時大家所看到的，假以時日，肯定成功。」<br />\n<br />\n外界盛傳球員對沙利已不再信任，但巴克里否認將帥不和：「在訓練場你可以看到，他嘗試令每一位球員進步，就像於拿玻里一樣。我們在過去數周一起經歷高低，有信心可以捱過。」"},{"pid":"f7f94493ab6986c285d960aa7772522a9331b0b7","tid":1034885,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"f05fad021905e94a57f4b4cb6dc5d372d86e4708","tid":1034885,"uid":33601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母巴狗"},{"pid":"9809e6a33d6aa7f064d89b876187a5da4ba685a1","tid":1034885,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05389081c6d73973596d1b0b89d3ae6b00a4362","tid":1034885,"uid":40422,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"今季在沙利麾下表現不錯的巴克里<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937c101592555fe4a92985f957b529c35fa1532b","tid":1034885,"uid":81273,"like":1,"